  "response": "Here are some signs that a guy might have a crush on you:\n\n1. Body Language Signals\n- Frequent eye contact\n- Leaning towards you when talking\n- Finding reasons to be physically close\n- Adjusting his appearance when you're around\n\n2. Communication Signs\n- Texts or calls more frequently\n- Shows genuine interest in your life\n- Remembers small details you've mentioned\n- Tries to make you laugh\n- Seeks your opinion on things\n\n3. Behavior Indicators\n- Seems nervous or shy around you\n- Gives you more attention than other friends\n- Finds excuses to spend time with you\n- Becomes protective of you\n- Gets jealous when you talk about other guys\n\n4. Emotional Clues\n- Compliments you often\n- Wants to help you with things\n- Seems more attentive and caring\n- Shows special consideration for your feelings\n\n5. Subtle Hints\n- Laughs at your jokes, even if they're not that funny\n- Tries to impress you\n- Mirrors your body language\n- Asks mutual friends about you\n\nRemember, these are just potential signs. The most reliable way to know is through direct communication.",
